Package: fwdreg
Title: Forward Selection for Regression Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Yiqiao", "Zhu", , "sgyzhu@umich.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provide a forward selection algorithm for building linear regression models.
    The process starts with a model containing only the intercept 
    and adds the most statistically significant predictor at each step 
    until no further improvement is seen in the AIC.
